title: Frida Baby Soother-Style Medicine Dispenser, Medi Frida Baby Medicine Syringe & Accu-Dose Soother, Baby Medicine Dispenser for Mess & Fuss Free Use
features: MESS & FUSS FREE: The soother-style baby medicine dispenser directs liquids to the side of the baby's cheek, effectively preventing spit-ups and ensuring a mess-free experience.
ACCURATE DOSING: Designed for accurate dosing the medicine dispenser bypasses the baby's tastebuds, making it ideal for administering medications, gripe water, vitamins, and various other liquids.

CONVENIENT SYRINGE: The included syringe features markings for common medicine doses, offering precise measurement for accurate dosing. Alternatively, any standard syringe can be used with the soother.

COMFORTABLE DESIGN: Crafted in the familiar soother shape used widely in hospitals across the nation, it provides a comfortable and reassuring experience for babies during medication administration. The dummy tab allows it to double as a real soother!
EVERYTHING YOU NEED: Each Medi Frida Accu-Dose Soother set includes 1 syringe, 1 soother and when combined is a soother medicine dispenser.
description: The FridaBaby MediFrida delivers baby the full dose of medicine without the spit up. The soft, familiar soother sends medicine to the side of the cheek and bypasses baby's taste buds to prevent spit-ups and allows baby to swallow the doctor's recommended dose. The MediFrida medicine soother is the only soother-style baby medicine dispenser that doubles as a real soother, so dosing doesn't disrupt baby's busy soothing schedule.
